:492592,"uid":30830,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T13:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/013749_82ef189d1a0226800d14c31cc144c454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F013749_82ef189d1a0226800d14c31cc144c454.jpg&h=f8e10dd1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文筆說不上極佳但至少中上<br />\n扣題清楚<br />\n創意十足<br />\n故事起承轉合完整<br />\n完全唔明點解自尋死路<br />\n<br />\n中三果陣我中二病發作考試都作到類似咁<br />\n結果考試唔合格<br />\n然後就知到班老古董淨係鍾意老掉牙嘅懶陽光正能量<br />\n跟住佢地心意咁寫，會考同高考嘅中文 /中化都a<br />\n但其實篇篇都一樣樣悶到仆街"},{"pid":"2236979e9cfb19430542b8a7432867d9bf5c74cc","tid":492592,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T13:59:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗起呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/013749_82ef189d1a0226800d14c31cc144c454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F013749_82ef189d1a0226800d14c31cc144c454.jpg&h=f8e10dd1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文筆說不上極佳但至少中上<br />\n扣題清楚<br />\n創意十足<br />\n故事起承轉合完整<br />\n完全唔明點解自尋死路<br />\n<br />\n中三果陣我中二病發作考試都作到類似咁<br />\n結果考試唔合格<br />\n然後就知<span style=\"color: red;\">道</span>班老古董淨係鍾意老掉牙嘅懶陽光正能量<br />\n跟住佢地心意咁寫，會考同高考嘅中文 /中化都a<br />\n但其實篇篇都一樣樣悶到仆街</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1456673116c6f25dd3452e1448560b293b35fbbf","tid":492592,"uid":34511,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗起呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/013749_82ef189d1a0226800d14c31cc144c454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h